Company Overview of Emerald Mutual Fund Advisers Trust



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Emerald Mutual Fund Advisers Trust is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to investment companies. It manages equity mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It conducts in-house research to make its investments. The firm is based in Lancaster, Pennsylvania. Emerald Mutual Fund Advisers Trust operates as a subsidiary of Emerald Advisers, Inc.


1703 Oregon PikeLancaster, PA 17601United States



Phone: 717-396-1116

Fax: 717-399-3140








